src/ts/components/DagFileTree.tsx.description:
DagFileTree visualizes a NetworkX Directed Acyclic Graph (DAG) as an interactive 
nested file tree with node selection capabilities.

data.description: The hierarchical tree data converted from a NetworkX DAG.

persistSelection.description: Whether to maintain selection state when expanding/collapsing nodes.

selectParents.description:
Whether to automatically select parent nodes when a child is selected
and deselect child nodes when a parent is deselected.

maxHeight.description: Maximum height of the tree container in pixels.

searchQuery.description: Optional search query to filter nodes in the tree.

debounceMs.description: Number of milliseconds to debounce search input changes.

id.description: Unique ID to identify this component in Dash callbacks.
